The comedy roller coaster starts with Kapil speaking and welcoming the great actor, Mithun Chakraborty. Kapil starts his interview and the question and answer session, has the audience in splits. During the interview, Kapil's wife comes on the stage and the usual tiff starts between him and his wife. A bit later, the great Bollywood director Subhash Ghai joins them on the stage for the promotion of his new forthcoming movie, Kaanchi. Finally, Mishti, the new face being introduced by Subhash Ghai along with the lead actor, Karthik, comes on the stage. Watch the episode and have a fun filled and rollicking time.
